Package: lisi
Type: Package
Title: Local neighborhood diversity for scRNAseq.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-03-31
Author: Ilya Korsunsky
Maintainer: Ilya Korsunsky <ilya.korsunsky@gmail.com>
Description: This method was designed to assess how well mixed cells with different labels are in single cell RNAseq. This method uses the Inverse Simpson's Index to compute diversity of each cells' neighborhood.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.2), RANN, ggplot2, dplyr, tidyr
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: testthat
LazyData: true
